{"tid":275651,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔寂滅 繼續柒]陳云根：港人在台尋政治庇護  台灣未試過將疑犯送回香港","createTime":"2017-06-08T07:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T10:16:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6084f29a006e48affe493e5a0a89f17b35d666a","tid":275651,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"你腦無！ 小草係點樣返去香港受審架？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160812/photo/bkn-20160812143910033-0812_00822_001_01p.jpg?20160812161755\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160812%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160812143910033-0812_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20160812161755&h=5adf1b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155292985737225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10155292985737225&d=CjW7Ylva%2FuVBik9pR%2Fkhn%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=2dd2383f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155292985737225</a><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：蔡英文總統遇到了困難了。香港人的居留地是香港特別行政區（香港城邦的憲法名稱），依照國際法，香港人只能被遞送回來香港，不能遣返到其他地區。然而，香港特別行政區與中華民國在台灣之間，並無引渡條例，也向來沒有司法互助關係。台灣可以將中國的政治庇護尋求者遞送回中國，中國依法收容，但台灣從未有將疑犯遞送回香港審理的先例，包括嚴重罪行的刑事疑犯，九七之前也沒有。台灣一直是香港人的司法避風港，在當中撈到不少好處，這是秘而不宣的事情。<br />\n<br />\n台灣一旦打破先例，在台灣躲藏的各種香港疑犯，不論被起訴的還是備案但沒起訴的，包括以前在香港涉嫌犯案而被港府記錄的台灣情報人員或涉事人員，這些以前英國殖民政府姑息但香港特區政府未必姑息的人員，例如有國民黨黨產而歸台的人員，只有符合香港的司法追溯期限，在必要時候將受到香港特別行政區的引渡要求，那麼國府以前在香港布下的網絡，在嚴峻的政治局面下，將被中共逐個用香港的惡法擊破。（當然，如果蔡英文總統與中國有默契，那就不必考慮這些台灣國家安全的事情。）<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文總統，請閣下慎重考慮。事情僵持不下的話，可以給美方駐台人員聯絡，轉送第三國。"},{"pid":"8e4310aaa6f62a39dc23d974fe6008ad2ff5494e","tid":275651,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20160812/large/1470986275_27f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20160812%2Flarge%2F1470986275_27f1.jpg&h=b80724bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2016/04/15/75834/i_640x640_704110526.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2016%2F04%2F15%2F75834%2Fi_640x640_704110526.jpg&h=94515083&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fac66f34315a4d019db6466e10215a43b696e98","tid":275651,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20160413/large/1460478136_58fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20160413%2Flarge%2F1460478136_58fa.jpg&h=970870fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20160413/large/1460478141_4aa0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20160413%2Flarge%2F1460478141_4aa0.jpg&h=f6d430b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20160413/large/1460532002_81f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20160413%2Flarge%2F1460532002_81f8.jpg&h=872a417d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0eac1ebba02c988315a7a22208c6b3bdd1f0d8df","tid":275651,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bca50b1c044c4ef49a15e2500958f526cb0504b","tid":275651,"uid":34377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:08:24.000Z","msg":"小草當時係謀殺案疑犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3c84816de386d7fcf0ecc3f5633c3054e07536","tid":275651,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017